Package: pipeflow
Title: Data Analysis Workflows with Pipelines
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R:
    person("Roman", "Pahl", , "roman.pahl@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simple but flexible framework for composing, combining and
    modifying custom data analysis pipelines. In nonlinear pipelines,
    dependencies among analysis steps are tracked and can be used to
    re-run only steps that are affected by changes.
License: MIT
Imports:
    data.table,
    jsonlite,
    lgr,
    methods,
    R6,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
